    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a reliable choice for someone looking for a functional car at an affordable price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scuffs on the bumpers and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it will eventually need attention for a minor oil leak and aging suspension components. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
